subsection.text:

  Section 1895(b)(3)(A)(iii) of the Social Security Act (
  42 U.S.C. 1395fff(b)(3)(A)(iii)
) is amended—


  Section 1895(b)(5)(A) of the Social Security Act (
  42 U.S.C. 1395fff(b)(5)(A)
) is amended, in the second sentence, by inserting (or, in the case of each of the years 2015 through 2023, 2.25 percent) after 2.5 percent.
